and type = 'U')

/* Table: busi_moveSKU */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_moveSKU (
MID int not null,
depotID nvarchar(20) null,
FLocation nvarchar(20) null,
TLocation nvarchar(20) null,
SkuID int null,
SkuCode nvarchar(30) null,
num int null,
apptime datetime null,
Ismove int null,
movetime datetime null,
constraint PK_BUSI_MOVESKU primary key (MID)
)
